_sText:
Dare ye enter the deepest, darkest lair of GRUDGE's mind?
We have drilled deep into his mind to bring back the precious substance, also known as camel-a-licious.
But the terrorist wish to destroy the very existence of this alternate world.
Yes, even teh bad guys want to destroy the mini city and the wine cellar!
While you are down there, don't get distracted by the beautiful celebrities and appearances by the likes of Queen, The White Stripes, Radiohead, and more!
Remember why you are here!
And while you are here, ask yourself the question:
"Why?"
Slouch in your chair and ponder.
Who knows, maybe you will even unlock the secret to this world and get to enjoy an epic chariot race, just like ancient times!
Fellow travelers, if ye dare enter beyond this point, beware, for you will discover that reality blends with dream, fact with fiction.
You may just lose yourself in the PARALLEL UNIVERSE.
